    "English": "A large and complex field-based subspace radar.<br><br>Due to its large power consumption and inherent subatomic instability, this technology must be mounted to an Exocraft.<br><br>Press <span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span> to activate the Signal Booster.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "大型复合实地子空间雷达。<br><br>由于巨大的能量消耗和内部亚原子不稳定性，该技术必须安装在强化艇上。<br><br>按下<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>来激活信号增强器。",
    "TencentChinese": "大型复合实地子空间雷达。<br> <br>由于其巨大的能量消耗和内部亚原子不稳定性，仅安装于强化艇上。<br><br>按 <span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span> 来激活信号推进器。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "大型複合精密亞空間雷達。<br><br>由於需消耗大量能源，且運作時會產生亞原子不穩定問題，這種科技只能安裝於強化艇上。<br><br>按下 <span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span> 來啟動訊號強化器。"
